            <div class=""sub_stand_out"">
                <h3 class=""small_heading""> II. 1. Origine of the program </h3>
                <p class=""description""> 
                    Human resources management plays a key role in the management processes of organizations and, for the most part, finds its origin in the
                    multidimensional activities of the organization. This finding challenges business leaders to have a management or service that will make
                    managing staff a concern for achieving their goals. The human resources management program responds to this need and is based on the lessons
                    of management or human resources management specialization programs. This ");
            WriteLiteral(@"program prepares students for the Bachelor of Management or
                    Human Resources Management cycle.
                </p>
            </div>

