                <h3 class=""smaller_heading""> II.2.1. General Objective </h3>
                <p class=""description""> 
                    The objective of this course is to train polyvalent graduates in the fields of human resources management with in particular strong knowledge in
                    the field of resource management; both men and equipment. At the end of this program, graduates will be able to use the skills acquired from
                    various private and public institutions but also from national and international non-governmental organizations.
                    
