                    <li> Accompany the company in mastering its challenges in human resources management; </li>
                    <li> Ensure the regular monitoring of personnel and material management in the various sites or specific missions; </li>
                    <li> Develop projected budgets in terms of salaries; </li>
                    <li> Control, verify, inspect, critically monitor the forward planning of jobs. </li>
                </ul>

